What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: The class is a lot of work but it is very rewarding at the end once you realized that the hard work put in pays off.
It's a lot of work, but all languages are. Overall I don't think it was as hard as L3, at least towards the end. I think L3 was a little bit more work too.
Take this class. You'll come out speaking more fluidly and with such increased reading skills.
Good course. I enjoyed the readings and films more in f130, but f140 does a great job of tackling some of the more nuanced aspects of French grammar.
